item.title: CVE-2021-21614|2024-08-03T18:16:23.659Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20bumblebee%20hp%20alm%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Bumblebee HP ALM Plugin 4.1.5 and earlier stores credentials unencrypted in its global configuration file on the Jenkins controller where they can be viewed by users with access to the Jenkins controller file system.
